title: [PS3] GameSonic Manager v3.10
description:
GameSonic Manager v3.10 - Orion adds a Spoof Installer/Removal feature / webMAN Mod plugin added to installer / Various GUI Changes and more
Developer Orion has also updated his Ps3 Backup Manager known as GameSonic Manager to version 3.10. In this update several new additions and various fixes have been applied in this update. Some highlights included: A new Spoof Installer/Remover for 4.46 - 4.55 CFW including Cobra CFW to 4.60, webMAN MOD has been added to the plugin installer found in this manager plus various other additions that can be found in the release quote from the developer.
